<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Google Gemma 4 開源大模型重磅發布 | AI News 專題報道</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-blue: #00d4ff;
            --primary-purple: #7b2cbf;
            --accent-red: #ff4757;
            --accent-green: #00ff88;
            --dark-bg: #0a0a0f;
            --card-bg: #12121a;
            --card-bg-light: #1a1a28;
            --text-primary: #ffffff;
            --text-secondary: #a0a0b0;
            --gradient-1: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff 0%, #7b2cbf 100%);
            --glow-blue: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.5);
            --glow-purple: 0 0 20px rgba(123, 44, 191, 0.5);
        }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body { font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif; background-color: var(--dark-bg); color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.8; overflow-x: hidden; }
        
        @keyframes float { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); } 50% { transform: translateY(-20px); } }
        @keyframes pulse { 0%, 100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.6; } }
        @keyframes slideIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
        @keyframes codeRain { 0% { transform: translateY(-100%); opacity: 0; } 10% { opacity: 1; } 90% { opacity: 1; } 100% { transform: translateY(100vh); opacity: 0; } }
        
        .code-rain { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; overflow: hidden; }
        .code-char { position: absolute; color: var(--primary-blue); font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0; animation: codeRain 4s linear infinite; }
        
        .hero { position: relative; min-height: 85vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 80px 20px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--dark-bg) 0%, #1a1a2e 100%); overflow: hidden; }
        .hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(123, 44, 191, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%); z-index: 1; }
        .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 1200px; text-align: center; animation: slideIn 1s ease-out; }
        .hero-badge { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 28px; background: var(--gradient-1); border-radius: 50px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 24px; box-shadow: var(--glow-blue); }
        .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 24px; background: var(--gradient-1); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; line-height: 1.3; }
        .hero-subtitle { font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.3rem); color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 40px; }
        .hero-image { margin-top: 50px; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--glow-purple); max-width: 900px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
        .hero-image img { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
        .scroll-indicator { position: absolute; bottom: 40px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); animation: float 2s ease-in-out infinite; z-index: 2; }
        .scroll-indicator span { display: block; width: 30px; height: 50px; border: 2px solid var(--primary-blue); border-radius: 25px; position: relative; }
        .scroll-indicator span::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 8px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 6px; height: 10px; background: var(--primary-blue); border-radius: 3px; animation: pulse 1.5s infinite; }
        
        section { padding: 80px 20px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
        .content-section { background: var(--card-bg); padding: 50px 40px; border-radius: 24px; border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2); max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto 40px; box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); }
        .content-section h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 30px; color: var(--primary-blue); padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3); }
        .content-section h3 { font-size: 1.4rem; margin: 35px 0 18px; color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: 600; }
        .content-section h4 { font-size: 1.15rem; margin: 25px 0 12px; color: var(--primary-blue); font-weight: 600; }
        .content-section p { color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .content-section ul { margin: 20px 0; padding-left: 30px; color: var(--text-secondary); }
        .content-section li { margin: 10px 0; line-height: 1.8; }
        .content-section strong { color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 600; }
        .content-section a { color: var(--primary-blue); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--primary-blue); }
        .content-section a:hover { border-bottom-style: solid; }
        
        .meta-info { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15) 0%, rgba(123, 44, 191, 0.15) 100%); padding: 25px 30px; border-radius: 16px; margin-bottom: 35px; border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-blue); }
        .meta-info p { margin: 10px 0; color: var(--text-secondary); }
        .meta-info strong { color: var(--primary-blue); }
        
        .model-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 25px; margin: 40px 0; }
        .model-card { background: var(--card-bg-light); padding: 30px; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }
        .model-card h4 { color: var(--accent-green); margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 1.2rem; }
        .model-card .spec { display: flex; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .model-card .spec span { background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15); padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--primary-blue); }
        .model-card ul { padding-left: 20px; margin: 0; }
        .model-card li { margin: 8px 0; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        
        .highlight-box { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.1) 0%, rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1) 100%); padding: 25px; border-radius: 16px; border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-green); margin: 30px 0; }
        .highlight-box h4 { color: var(--accent-green); margin-bottom: 15px; }
        
        footer { background: #050508; padding: 60px 20px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }
        footer p { color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .footer-links { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 30px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .footer-links a { color: var(--primary-blue); text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="code-rain" id="codeRain"></div>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <span class="hero-badge">📰 AI News 專題報道</span>
            <h1>Google Gemma 4 開源大模型重磅發布</h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">31B 參數挑戰百億巨獸，端側 AI 新紀元</p>
            <div class="hero-image">
                <img src="./20260405_1107_img1.png" alt="Google Gemma 4 AI 模型">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="scroll-indicator"><span></span></div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <div class="content-section">
            <div class="meta-info">
                <p><strong>📺 來源</strong>：<a href="https://youtu.be/iqCr_pudCAA" target="_blank">YouTube 影片</a></p>
                <p><strong>📅 發布日期</strong>：2026年4月初</p>
